## Summary

This documentation page describes the HTTP V2 API for sending event data directly from servers to Amplitude's HTTP V2 endpoint, which replaces the deprecated HTTP API. It covers request/response formats, event payload structure, upload limits, data validation rules, error handling, and includes comprehensive examples for different request types.

